{"tid":1263573,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"七月新片《耶穌真係落左黎》","createTime":"2019-06-28T09:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T05:32:04.000Z","uid":41343,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2d472702059ea3385703bcf56345d69a19506846","tid":1263573,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"故事簡介<br />\n21歲天才導演奧山大史首部長片憑童真看人生，即勇奪西班牙聖塞巴斯蒂安電影節最佳新導演！小男孩一家搬到鄉郊生活，沒宗教信仰卻被送入基督教學校讀書，正感徬徨無助之際，迷你版耶穌卻突然顯現眼前！這個小耶穌會打相撲又會變法，對男孩可謂有求必應！但此時男孩的朋友卻遭逢意外，令他對神的信任開始動搖&hellip;&hellip;康城金棕櫚大獎得主是枝裕和盛讚有趣之作，當然不容錯過！<br />\n<br />\n導演<br />\n奥山大史<br />\n<br />\n演員<br />\n佐藤結良、大熊理樹、查德穆朗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1PUZ4PC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1PUZ4PC.jpg&h=e07c28ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ae97e0672aa85c54306b41be17a48def6a5fa2a","tid":1263573,"uid":39365,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"叫你既耶穌黎見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ea344c7010ee43df477f48a675f807e866f301","tid":1263573,"uid":49391,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4ae97e0672aa85c54306b41be17a48def6a5fa2a","tid":1263573,"uid":39365,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"叫你既耶穌黎見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"見到標題真係諗到呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n譯戲名條友本身係咪都係想影射呢件事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4adf1ddaecf5164f69520afa202c5c620251b29","tid":1263573,"uid":34409,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"17ea344c7010ee43df477f48a675f807e866f301","tid":1263573,"uid":49391,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4ae97e0672aa85c54306b41be17a48def6a5fa2a","tid":1263573,"uid":39365,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"